name: Summarize Agent
description: A rule for summarizing the actions and decisions of an agent.
---

- Summaries must include:
  - What was done during the entire conversation
  - What decisions were made
  - What still needs to be done
  - A detailed plan and checklist for implementation

<example>
Agent summarizes a refactor by listing all changes, decisions, remaining tasks, and a step-by-step plan.
</example>
<example type="invalid">
Agent provides a vague summary without details or a checklist.
</example>
